Introduction

Nagomi is a dancer and singer under 143 Entertainment. She is a member of the girl group MADEIN.

On September 2, 2023, Nagomi was revealed as a contestant on the survival show "PRODUCE 101 JAPAN THE GIRLS". She was eliminated in the tenth episode, during the third ranking announcement, after placing 23rd overall.

On May 10, 2024, Nagomi was announced as a new member of the girl group MAIDEN under 143 Entertainment.
